name: RadiantDaydream#10
description:
This Interactive NFT changes when viewed at different moments of the Diurnal cycle. 
Between 19:00 and 6:00 the blue glow shifts to night mode.

RadiantDaydream#10 features a portal within the Dreamverse, something seems to be interfering with the viewers perception resulting in an interpolated optical glitch likely the work of Dreamrealm entity~#3 'The GlitzBeast"
 
"DAY NIGHT" is open source for hicetnunc nft creators coded by @Voltaine1 https://github.com/voltaine1/daynight
